 My Personal and Academic Goals for Next Year

Complete My Current Research Project
Finalize and publish findings on illegal mining and deforestation in my community.

Improve My Technical Skills
Learn and apply digital tools (e.g., data analysis, GIS, or low-code platforms) to support research and solution design.

Apply for Internship or Job Opportunities
Gain hands-on experience in a tech or sustainability-focused role to bridge theory and practice.

Strengthen My Public Speaking & Communication Skills
Participate in seminars or pitch events to present research findings and build confidence.

Build a Community Initiative or Campaign
Launch or support a local campaign to raise awareness and encourage youth-led environmental protection.
